@startuml STM32 to STM32 Full Zephyr Pipeline

title STM32 → STM32 → STM32 (All Zephyr RTOS)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Monospaced
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam ArrowColor #444441
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor<<stm32>> #EEEDFE
    BorderColor<<stm32>> #534AB7
    FontColor<<stm32>> #26215C

    BackgroundColor<<ethernet>> #E1F5EE
    BorderColor<<ethernet>> #0F6E56
    FontColor<<ethernet>> #04342C

    BackgroundColor<<bus>> #FAEEDA
    BorderColor<<bus>> #BA7517
    FontColor<<bus>> #412402
}

'--- STM32 #1 (Source) ---
package "STM32 #1\n(Zephyr RTOS)" <<stm32>> {
    component [CAN1 TX\nt₀: send] as STM1_TX <<stm32>>
    component [CAN2 RX\nt₃: receive] as STM1_RX <<stm32>>
}

'--- STM32 #2 (Gateway 1) ---
package "STM32 #2\n(Zephyr RTOS)" <<stm32>> {
    component [CAN1 RX] as STM2_CAN <<stm32>>
    component [Zephyr Open1722\nEncapsulate] as STM2_ENC <<stm32>>
    component [Ethernet TX\n+ LAN8720 PHY] as STM2_ETH <<stm32>>
}

'--- STM32 #3 (Gateway 2) ---
package "STM32 #3\n(Zephyr RTOS)" <<stm32>> {
    component [Ethernet RX\n+ LAN8720 PHY] as STM3_ETH <<stm32>>
    component [Zephyr Open1722\nDecapsulate] as STM3_DEC <<stm32>>
    component [CAN2 TX] as STM3_CAN <<stm32>>
}

'--- Buses ---
component [CAN Bus A\n250 kbps] as CANA <<bus>>
component [CAN Bus B\n250 kbps] as CANB <<bus>>
component [Ethernet\nDirect Cable\nIEEE-1722] as ETH <<ethernet>>

'--- Flow ---
STM1_TX --> CANA : t₀
CANA --> STM2_CAN
STM2_CAN --> STM2_ENC
STM2_ENC --> STM2_ETH
STM2_ETH --> ETH : IEEE-1722\nAVTP
ETH --> STM3_ETH
STM3_ETH --> STM3_DEC
STM3_DEC --> STM3_CAN
STM3_CAN --> CANB
CANB --> STM1_RX : t₃

note bottom of STM1_TX
    **Pure RTOS Environment**
    No Linux scheduler jitter
    Expected: 30-50% latency reduction
    Requires: 3× STM32F439ZI + 2× LAN8720
end note

@enduml
